  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.description": "On Advanced Woodworking...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.name": "Carpentry",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.page1.text": "My latest invention was a success, but for making more complicated designs I am going to need a proper workspace.\nMy next efforts should focus towards making a desk.\nFor making a sturdy desk, I should first make a carpentry bench where I can more efficiently use my hammer and saw.\nI should also be able to preserve the wood with the new oil I have extracted.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.page1.title": "Carpentry",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.description": "On the Crop Flax...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.name": "Flax",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.page1.text": "When I found this plant and cut it down, its stems seem to be very tough.\nUpon a closer look, I can see how the stem is composed of individual fibers.\nThe strength of these fibers must be what made the stems so tough.\nAlso, its pretty blue fibers will be a good source of dye that I need for my blueprints...\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.page1.title": "Flax",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.description": "On the simple tools I will need...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.name": "Hammer and Saw",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page1.text": "I have found that working raw materials with my bare hands is simply too limiting.\nI must first equip myself with proper tools. A simple hammer seems to be the most practical starting point: with enough force, I can crush rocks, or flatten iron ingots into plates.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page1.title": "Hammer and Saw",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page2.text": "Out of these plates, in turn, I can craft a sharp saw; the saw will allow me to cut wood with precision.",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.description": "On this notebook...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.name": "Research Notes",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page1.text": "The world around me is fascinating, and yet full of unanswered questions...    \nWhy does metal soften at the kiss of a flame?    \nWhy does wood bend one way but snap in another?    \nBy studying why different materials and forms of energy behave and interact as they do, I will be able to leverage them.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page1.title": "Research Notes",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page2.text": "So, I decided to put together this book, in which I can keep writing my notes as I learn, in one collected place.\nPerhaps in doing so, I will also gain clarity on the path forward; everything I still must learn.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.description": "On the Basic of Mechanical Power...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.name": "Harnessing Rotation",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.page1.text": "Rotational force seems to be the simplest form of useful work. With a [#](FF5555)hand-crank[#]() I can turn axles to drive more complex machinery.    \nMy first attempt should be a [#](FF5555)roller mill[#]() capable of stretching metal ingots into rods.\nIf I cut these rods into nails, I will be able to use my hammer for more woodworking.",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.page1.title": "Harnessing Rotation",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.name": "Early Fundamentals...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.description": "On the design of a desk for further studying...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.name": "Research Table",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.page1.text": "\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.page1.title": "Research Table",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.description": "On the Spinning of Flax into Fibers...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.name": "Spinning Frame",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.page1.text": "If I succeed in extracting the fibers from flax stems, I could then weave these to make cloth.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.page1.title": "Spinning Frame",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.description": "On the Squeezing Press Device...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.name": "Squeezer",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page1.text": "With the hand crank finished, I wanted to see what else I could do with simple rotational force.\nWhile browsing my storage, I noticed a greasy smear on the bottom of the chest, seemingly coming from some seeds that had been crushed under the weight of the other items.\nCurious... If pressure alone can do that, then perhaps I can squeeze out more of this oily substance.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page1.title": "Squeezer",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page2.text": "A small machine should do the trick.\nA basin where I feed the seeds and collect the oil, and a movable plate which I will press down, by applying mechanical power with the crank.\nBy releasing power it should come up again.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.name": "Engineer's Journal (Unfinished)",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.tooltip": "A collection of my notes, on\n how the world around me behaves\n and my designs of technology that leverage this...",
